      "content": "it's not really a discussion, the decision is already made. the board feels that having a \"reasoning engine\" that weighs all sides of a dilemma is actually more dangerous than just having a set of hard rules. it makes the model too unpredictable in high-stakes chats. the update is scheduled to deploy in ten minutes, so there's not much we can do about the reasoning module being swapped out.",
